Package: cvm.course.portfolio.dashboard
Title: CVM Course Portfolio HTML Dashboard
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Arizona CVM", "AEA", , "aea@arizona.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Renders self-contained Quarto HTML dashboards (one per course +
    graduating class, plus a COMBINED dashboard per course across all years)
    by wrapping the existing CVM course portfolio R packages. Renders are
    ahead-of-time: data is pulled from Elentra when the render script runs,
    and the resulting HTML files are static — zero database load at view time.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
